{
  "info": {
    "name": "MG Plastic — Store Registration (Retail vs Wholesale)",
    "_postman_id": "d4e5f6a7-regstore-4000-9000-mgstorereg",
    "description": "# تسجيل المتاجر من الموبايل\n\n## المهم للموبايل\nاستخدم **فقط**:\n\n`POST /api/v1/auth/register-retail`\n\n→ ينشئ `role = retail_trader` (تاجر تجزئة / قطاعي)\n\n**لا تستخدم** `register-store` من شاشة تسجيل المتاجر في الموبايل — ده لـ **موزّع الجملة** (`wholesale_distributor`).\n\nAlias بنفس السلوك: `POST /api/v1/auth/register-trader`\n\n## التدفق\n1. Register Retail (multipart أو JSON)\n2. Verify OTP\n3. انتظر موافقة الأدمن (`is_approved`)\n4. Login → استخدم `my-store/*`\n\n## Content-Type\n- بدون صور: `application/json`\n- مع صور: `multipart/form-data`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://mg-plastic.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "retail_name", "value": "محل تجريبي قطاعي", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "retail_phone", "value": "0912000001", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "retail_password", "value": "secret123", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "retail_email", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "retail_brand_name", "value": "براند تجريبي", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "retail_address", "value": "طرابلس - ليبيا", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "country_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "city_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "latitude", "value": "32.8872", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "longitude", "value": "13.1913", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "otp", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "store_user_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "wholesale_phone", "value": "0912000002", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "wholesale_password", "value": "secret123", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1 — Retail (تاجر تجزئة) — USE THIS ON MOBILE",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Retail — JSON (minimal)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "const token = json?.data?.token;",
                  "const store = json?.data?.store;",
                  "if (token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                  "if (store?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('store_user_id', String(store.id));",
                  "pm.test('created as retail_trader', () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(201);",
                  "  pm.expect(store?.role).to.eql('retail_trader');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"{{retail_name}}\",\n  \"phone\": \"{{retail_phone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{retail_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register-retail",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register-retail"]
            },
            "description": "**الصح للموبايل.**\n\nRequired: `name`, `phone`, `password`\n\nResponse `data.store.role` يجب أن يكون `retail_trader` و `network_code` مثل `MG-R-000xxx`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register Retail — JSON (full profile)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json?.data?.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "if (json?.data?.store?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('store_user_id', String(json.data.store.id));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"{{retail_name}}\",\n  \"phone\": \"{{retail_phone}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{retail_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{retail_password}}\",\n  \"brand_name\": \"{{retail_brand_name}}\",\n  \"address\": \"{{retail_address}}\",\n  \"store_description\": \"متجر قطاعي لمواد السباكة\",\n  \"short_description\": \"تجزئة MG Plastic\",\n  \"long_description\": \"وصف أطول للمتجر يظهر في الملف العام بعد الموافقة.\",\n  \"website\": \"https://example.com\",\n  \"country_id\": {{country_id}},\n  \"city_id\": {{city_id}},\n  \"latitude\": {{latitude}},\n  \"longitude\": {{longitude}},\n  \"social_links\": [\n    { \"platform\": \"facebook\", \"url\": \"https://facebook.com/mystore\", \"sort_order\": 0 },\n    { \"platform\": \"whatsapp\", \"url\": \"https://wa.me/218912000001\", \"sort_order\": 1 }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register-retail",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register-retail"]
            },
            "description": "كل الحقول الاختيارية + social_links.\n\nملاحظة: `website` و `social_links.*.url` لازم URL كامل يبدأ بـ https:// في الـ validation الحالي."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register Retail — multipart (with photos)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json?.data?.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "if (json?.data?.store?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('store_user_id', String(json.data.store.id));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "name", "value": "{{retail_name}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "phone", "value": "{{retail_phone}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "password", "value": "{{retail_password}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "brand_name", "value": "{{retail_brand_name}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "address", "value": "{{retail_address}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "country_id", "value": "{{country_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "city_id", "value": "{{city_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "latitude", "value": "{{latitude}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "longitude", "value": "{{longitude}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "profile_photo", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "اختياري — صورة الملف" },
                { "key": "brand_logo", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "اختياري — شعار المتجر" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register-retail",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register-retail"]
            },
            "description": "multipart/form-data لرفع الصور. اختَر ملفات لـ profile_photo و brand_logo في Postman."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register Retail — alias register-trader",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"{{retail_name}}\",\n  \"phone\": \"{{retail_phone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{retail_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register-trader",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register-trader"]
            },
            "description": "نفس `register-retail` بالظبط (alias)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify OTP",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "const token = json?.token || json?.data?.token;",
                  "if (token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{retail_phone}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"{{otp}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/verify-otp",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "verify-otp"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Resend OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{retail_phone}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/resend-otp",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "resend-otp"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Retail",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "const token = json?.data?.token || json?.token;",
                  "if (token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{retail_phone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{retail_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "My Store (after login)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/my-store",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "my-store"]
            },
            "description": "تأكد إن `role` = `retail_trader`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Public store profile (after admin approval)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/network-stores/{{store_user_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "network-stores", "{{store_user_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "يستخدم User ID (مش plumber-stores id). قبل الموافقة → 404 غير متاح."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2 — Wholesale (موزّع جملة) — NOT for retail mobile screen",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Wholesale (register-store)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"موزع جملة تجريبي\",\n  \"phone\": \"{{wholesale_phone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{wholesale_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register-store",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register-store"]
            },
            "description": "⚠️ هذا ينشئ `wholesale_distributor`.\nلا تستخدمه في شاشة تسجيل تاجر التجزئة بالموبايل.\nنفس الحقول الاختيارية زي register-retail."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3 — Field reference",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET countries (for country_id)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/countries",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "countries"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET cities (for city_id)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/cities?country_id={{country_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "cities"],
              "query": [{ "key": "country_id", "value": "{{country_id}}" }]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
